{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181640/extras/SteamStoreBanner_Exhibited.png?t=1638207969\" /><br><i>Project Exhibited is a student-made game by Breda University of Applied Sciences.</i><br><br>In Project Exhibited, a thrilling first-person action-stealth game, you play as Dana, the inventor thief. You have been tasked to steal from a private art collection in a mysterious palazzo. <br><br>You put your mastery of stealth to the test in a tense mission.<br>Armed with an arsenal of advanced gadgets, you dodge security systems, outsmart the guards and make some interesting discoveries. <br>There might be more to these artifacts than meets the eye\u2026<br><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1181640/extras/SteamStoreBanner_Features.png?t=1638207969\" /><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Open-Ended Level Design</h2>We offer freedom of choice with our open-ended level design that allows you to complete the level how you want. Choose your own path through the palazzo and past the guards.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Dynamic Score System</h2>We measure your success through a dynamic score system. Were you aggressive, or super sneaky? Did you disable all security? You can even compete with other players for the high scores!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"> Intelligent Guards</h2>Our guards and security systems will react to your actions. They cooperate and will scout for you when they see you. Analyze their routines and maybe you can outsmart them.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Unique Gadget System</h2>You are an inventor, so obviously you crafted some gadgets. Use them to outplay the guards, knock them out, distract them, short-circuit electronics and plan your path!","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Shocking development","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1181640/ef4aa5471e2a28ab8cf108d693f0b70c83f3cc41.jpg"},{"name":"A H